      "title": "Mayonnaise Machine",
      "pageid": 2093,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Mayonnaise Machine</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Mayonnaise_Machine.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise Machine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/ef/Mayonnaise_Machine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Turns eggs into mayonnaise.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><i>Cannot be sold</i>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Crafting</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Recipe Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Farming Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Farming\" title=\"Farming\">Farming</a>&#160;(Level 2)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Ingredients</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(15)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(15)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Earth Crystal.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/74/Earth_Crystal.png/24px-Earth_Crystal.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/74/Earth_Crystal.png/36px-Earth_Crystal.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/74/Earth_Crystal.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Earth_Crystal\" title=\"Earth Crystal\">Earth Crystal</a>&#160;(1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Copper Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/24px-Copper_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/36px-Copper_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Copper_Bar\" title=\"Copper Bar\">Copper Bar</a>&#160;(1)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Mayonnaise Machine</b> is a type of <a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan Equipment</a> used to make <a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>.  It takes eggs and turns them into various kinds of <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Products\">Products</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mayonnaise_Machine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Products\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/Animal_Products_Profitability\" title=\"Animal Products Profitability\">Animal Products Profitability</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Regular white or brown chicken <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">eggs</a> produce normal quality Mayonnaise, and <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large white or brown chicken eggs</a> produce gold-quality mayonnaise. A single <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a> will produce 10 jars of Mayonnaise, with the quality of the Mayonnaise equal to the quality of the Ostrich Egg used. A <a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a> will produce three gold-quality Mayonnaise.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Ingredient\n</th>\n<th>Processing Time<sup id=\"cite_ref-processtime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-processtime-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th>\n<th>Energy\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Mayonnaise.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a>\n</td>\n<td>It looks spreadable.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span> <i>or</i><br /><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span> <i>or</i> <br /><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Ostrich Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/24px-Ostrich_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png/36px-Ostrich_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Ostrich_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span> <i>or</i> <br /><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Golden Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/97/Golden_Egg.png/24px-Golden_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/97/Golden_Egg.png/36px-Golden_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/97/Golden_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 3 Hours</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/24px-Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/36px-Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>190g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/24px-Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/36px-Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>237g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/24px-Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/36px-Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>285g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/24px-Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png/36px-Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>380g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r121010\">.mw-parser-output .energytemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .energytemplate img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"energytemplate\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/24px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/36px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a9/Energy.png 2x\" />50</span><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r121017\">.mw-parser-output .healthtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .healthtemplate img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"healthtemplate\"><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/24px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/36px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Health.png 2x\" />22</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Duck_Mayonnaise.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Duck Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Duck_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's a rich, yellow mayonnaise.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 3 Hours</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/23/Duck_Mayonnaise.png/24px-Duck_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/23/Duck_Mayonnaise.png/36px-Duck_Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/23/Duck_Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>375g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r121010\"/><span class=\"energytemplate\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/24px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/36px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a9/Energy.png 2x\" />75</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r121017\"/><span class=\"healthtemplate\"><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/24px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/36px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Health.png 2x\" />33</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Void_Mayonnaise.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Void Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td>\n<td>A thick, black paste that smells like burnt hair.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Void Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Void_Egg.png/24px-Void_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Void_Egg.png/36px-Void_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/58/Void_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 3 Hours</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Void Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png/24px-Void_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png/36px-Void_Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f3/Void_Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>275g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r121010\"/><span class=\"energytemplate\"><img alt=\"Poison.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/05/Poison.png/24px-Poison.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/05/Poison.png/36px-Poison.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/05/Poison.png 2x\" />&#160;−75</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c3/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's thick and creamy, with a vivid green hue. It smells like grass and leather.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dinosaur Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png/24px-Dinosaur_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png/36px-Dinosaur_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 3 Hours</span>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png/24px-Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c3/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png/36px-Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c3/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>800g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r121010\"/><span class=\"energytemplate\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/24px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/36px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a9/Energy.png 2x\" />125</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r121017\"/><span class=\"healthtemplate\"><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/24px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/36px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Health.png 2x\" />56</span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mayonnaise_Machine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-processtime-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-processtime_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mayonnaise_Machine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Added <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a> recipe.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Added <a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> recipe. Mayonnaise Machines can now be stacked in a player's <a href=\"/Inventory\" title=\"Inventory\">inventory</a> and in <a href=\"/Chest\" title=\"Chest\">chests</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Added <a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a> and <a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a> recipe.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Mayonnaise is now edible. Mayonnaise Machines that are ready-to-harvest now show the quality star of the Mayonnaise.</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Equipment\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a> • <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> • <a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a> • <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a> • <a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</td></tr>\n