      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Mayonnaise Machine\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|recipe      = {{Name|Farming Skill Icon|link=Farming|Level 2}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|15}}{{Name|Stone|15}}{{Name|Earth Crystal|1}}{{Name|Copper Bar|1}}\n|sellprice   = Cannot be sold\n}}\nThe '''Mayonnaise Machine''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] used to make [[Artisan Goods]].  It takes eggs and turns them into various kinds of [[Mayonnaise]].\n\n==Products==\n:''See also: [[Animal Products Profitability]]''\nRegular white or brown chicken [[egg]]s produce normal quality Mayonnaise, and [[Large Egg|Large white or brown chicken eggs]] produce gold-quality mayonnaise. A single [[Ostrich Egg]] will produce 10 jars of Mayonnaise, with the quality of the Mayonnaise equal to the quality of the Ostrich Egg used. A [[Golden Egg]] will produce three gold-quality Mayonnaise.\n\n<!--Note: This section is transcluded on the Artisan Goods page-->\n<section begin=\"mmproducts\" />\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredient\n!Processing Time<noinclude><ref name=\"processtime\"/></noinclude>\n!Sell Price\n!Energy\n|-\n|[[File:Mayonnaise.png|center]]\n|[[Mayonnaise]]\n|{{Description|Mayonnaise}}\n|{{Name|Egg|1|class=inline}} ''or''<br />{{Name|Large Egg|1|class=inline}} ''or'' <br />{{Name|Ostrich Egg|1|class=inline}} ''or'' <br />{{Name|Golden Egg|1|class=inline}}\n|{{duration|3 Hours}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Mayonnaise|190|dsv=false}}\n|{{energy|50}}{{health|22}}\n|-\n|[[File:Duck Mayonnaise.png|center]]\n|[[Duck Mayonnaise]]\n|{{Description|Duck Mayonnaise}}\n|{{Name|Duck Egg|1}}\n|{{Duration|3 Hours}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Duck Mayonnaise|375|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{energy|75}}{{health|33}}\n|-\n|[[File:Void Mayonnaise.png|center]]\n|[[Void Mayonnaise]]\n|{{Description|Void Mayonnaise}}\n|{{Name|Void Egg|1}}\n|{{Duration|3 Hours}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Void Mayonnaise|275|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{energy|−75}}\n|-\n|[[File:Dinosaur Mayonnaise.png|center]]\n|[[Dinosaur Mayonnaise]]\n|{{Description|Dinosaur Mayonnaise}}\n|{{Name|Dinosaur Egg|1}}\n|{{Duration|3 Hours}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Dinosaur Mayonnaise|800|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{energy|125}}{{health|56}}\n|-\n|}<section end=\"mmproducts\" />\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Added [[Void Mayonnaise]] recipe.}}\n{{History|1.4|Added [[Dinosaur Mayonnaise]] recipe. Mayonnaise Machines can now be stacked in a player's [[inventory]] and in [[Chest|chests]].}}\n{{History|1.5|Added [[Ostrich Egg]] and [[Golden Egg]] recipe.}}\n{{History|1.6|Mayonnaise is now edible. Mayonnaise Machines that are ready-to-harvest now show the quality star of the Mayonnaise.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Mayonnaise-Maschine]]\n[[es:Mayonesera]]\n[[fr:Machine à mayonnaise]]\n[[it:Macchina per la maionese]]\n[[ja:マヨネーズマシン]]\n[[ko:마요네즈 기계]]\n[[hu:Majonézkészítő]]\n[[pt:Máquina de maionese]]\n[[ru:Майонезный автомат]]\n[[tr:Mayonez Makinesi]]\n[[zh:蛋黄酱机]]"
